---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
---
<BaseLayout
  title="James Allardyce | Urban Planning Proposals"
  description="Implementation-focused urban planning proposals: transportation, safety, public space, and long-term economic value."
  currentPath={currentPath}
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Urban planning proposals for safer, more functional cities</h1>
    <p>
      I publish implementation-focused proposals that improve mobility, safety, public space, and long-term economic outcomes.
      Chicago is the primary case study, but the principles are broadly applicable.
    </p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="button primary" href="/proposals/">View proposals</a>
      <a class="button" href="/proposals/lake-shore-drive/">Read the Lake Shore Drive plan</a>
      <a class="button" href="/about/">About</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card half">
      <h2>Featured proposal</h2>
      <p><strong>Reimagining Lake Shore Drive as a Destination, Not a Highway</strong></p>
      <p class="muted">Remove Outer Lake Shore Drive, convert Inner Lake Shore Drive into a bus-focused, emergency-accessible corridor, and redesign the lakefront as a connected civic asset.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px"><a href="/proposals/lake-shore-drive/">Read proposal →</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card half">
      <h2>How proposals are written</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Each proposal includes: an executive summary, the problem statement, what changes, expected outcomes (mobility, safety, economic),
        an implementation approach, and assumptions/open questions.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px"><a href="/proposals/">Browse proposals →</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Core themes</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Transportation performance • Public safety • Land use and opportunity cost • Public space • Implementation and phasing
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
